〈'''危機將至'''〉（{{lang-en|"Writing's on the Wall"}}）是英国发片艺人[[山姆·史密斯_(歌手)|山姆·史密斯]]演唱的歌曲，该曲系2015年[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|詹姆斯·邦德]]电影《[[007：幽灵党|007：幽灵党]]》的主题曲。该曲于2015年9月25日以[[数字音乐下载|-{zh-cn:数字下载渠道;zh-tw:數位下載管道;zh-hk:數碼下載渠道;}-]]发行<ref>{{cite web|title=Sam Smith’s ‘Writing’s on the Wall’ Is the Theme of New Bond Film Spectre|url=http://time.com/4024712/sam-smith-james-bond-theme-spectre-writings-on-the-wall/|publisher=time.com|accessdate=2015-09-08|archive-date=2015-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908235857/http://time.com/4024712/sam-smith-james-bond-theme-spectre-writings-on-the-wall/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。山姆·史密斯和{{le|吉米·内普斯|Jimmy Napes}}共同创作和制作了这首歌，[[解密兄弟|解密兄弟]]亦参与创作。歌曲获得的评价褒贬不一，特别是在被拿来跟以往的邦德电影主题作比较时<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34357110|title=Sam Smith Bond song splits opinion|work=BBC News|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925210138/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34357110|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2015/sep/25/sam-smith-james-bond-theme-writing-on-the-wall|title=Sam Smith’s James Bond theme review – ‘It feels like an X Factor ballad’|first=Alexis|last=Petridis|work=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925211354/http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2015/sep/25/sam-smith-james-bond-theme-writing-on-the-wall|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/09/25/sam-smith-writings-on-the-wall-james-bond-song-spectre_n_8194356.html|title=Sam Smith's 'Writing On The Wall' 'Spectre' Song Hasn't Impressed 'James Bond' Fans|work=The Huffington Post UK|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925220230/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/09/25/sam-smith-writings-on-the-wall-james-bond-song-spectre_n_8194356.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/trending/sam-smith-spectre-bond-writing-s-on-the-wall-1.3243418|title=The Writing's on the Wall: Sam Smith's James Bond Spectre theme panned online|date=2015-09-25|work=cbc.ca|access-date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130136/https://www.cbc.ca/news/trending/sam-smith-spectre-bond-writing-s-on-the-wall-1.3243418|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对歌曲的辨证评价使得[[雪莉·贝西|雪莉·贝西]]在歌曲发布当天荣登[[Twitter|Twitter]]趋势榜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/sam-smiths-james-bond-theme-song-writings-on-the-wall-makes-shirley-bassey-trend-on-twitter-because-people-hate-it-10516519.html|title=Sam Smith's James Bond theme song 'Writing's On The Wall' makes Shirley Bassey trend on Twitter because people hate it|work=The Independent|access-date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927213312/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/sam-smiths-james-bond-theme-song-writings-on-the-wall-makes-shirley-bassey-trend-on-twitter-because-people-hate-it-10516519.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/sam-smith/news/sam-smith-releases-new-bond-theme-but-twitter-reckons-hes-no-shirley-bassey|title=Sam Smith Releases New Bond Theme But Twitter Reckons He's No Shirley Bassey|work=MTV UK|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925212238/http://www.mtv.co.uk/sam-smith/news/sam-smith-releases-new-bond-theme-but-twitter-reckons-hes-no-shirley-bassey|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该单曲成为首支在[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]位列榜首的邦德电影主题曲。获得[[第73届金球奖|第73届金球奖]]、[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳原创歌曲。

== 背景 ==
史密斯和{{le|吉米·内普斯|Jimmy Napes}}共同创作<ref name="Guardian">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/sep/25/hear-sam-smith-bond-theme-writings-on-the-wall-spectre|title=Sam Smith's new Bond theme, Writing's on the Wall - listen here|author=Guardian music|work=The Guardian|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111928/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/sep/25/hear-sam-smith-bond-theme-writings-on-the-wall-spectre|dead-url=no}}</ref>。史密斯表示歌曲在一个旋风般的会议中形成。他和搭档吉米在半个小时内寫了这首歌，并迅速录制了[[样本唱片|样本]]<ref name="NPR">{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2015/09/25/442558641/hear-sam-smith-break-down-his-bond-theme-writings-on-the-wall?utm_medium=RSS&utm_campaign=music|title=Hear Sam Smith Break Down His Bond Theme, 'Writing's On The Wall'|author=NPR staff|work=''NPR''|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925203129/http://www.npr.org/2015/09/25/442558641/hear-sam-smith-break-down-his-bond-theme-writings-on-the-wall?utm_medium=RSS&utm_campaign=music|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当他们重新听录音时，他们非常对史密斯的声乐表现非常满意，在最终发行时终于用了这首歌——尽管在编曲时加了一些肌肉。2015年9月8日，史密斯宣布他将演唱詹姆斯·邦德电影《幽灵党》的主题曲。他表示表演主题曲是“我职业生涯的亮点之一”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://instagram.com/p/7XEimKx2S7/|title=Instagram|work=Instagram|access-date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130052921/https://www.instagram.com/p/7XEimKx2S7/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 创作 ==
歌曲以每分钟66拍的[[F小调|F小调]]创作。史密斯的音域从[[A♭_(音名)|A ♭<sub>4</sub>]]升至[[D♭_(音名)|D♭<sub>6</sub>]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0155669|publisher=Salli Isaak Music Publishing|accessdate=2015-09-25|title='Writing's on the Wall' sheet music|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129082825/https://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0155669|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
歌曲发行时获得乐评人的评价褒贬不一。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的亚历克西斯·佩特里蒂斯（{{lang|en|Alexis Petridis}}）写道：“〈危機將至〉尝试捕捉[[阿黛尔|阿黛尔]]的〈天幕杀机〉主题曲的情感，但因山姆·史密斯表示歌曲用20分钟写就而大打折扣<ref>{{cite web|title=Sam Smith's James Bond theme review – 'It feels like an X Factor ballad'|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2015/sep/25/sam-smith-james-bond-theme-writing-on-the-wall|website=The Guardian|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925211354/http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2015/sep/25/sam-smith-james-bond-theme-writing-on-the-wall|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]的刘易斯·康纳尔（{{lang|en|Lewis Corner}}）给出3/5星<ref>{{cite web|title=This week's new singles reviewed: Little Mix, Sia, Sam Smith, Rudimental|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/feature/a670557/this-weeks-new-singles-reviewed-little-mix-sia-sam-smith-rudimental.html#~ppQ1lkQ4pEzlux|website=Digital Spy|date=2015-09-25|access-date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031080811/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/feature/a670557/this-weeks-new-singles-reviewed-little-mix-sia-sam-smith-rudimental.html#~ppQ1lkQ4pEzlux|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的聂耳·麦考密克（{{lang|en|Neil McCormick}}）称这首歌是“邦德民谣怪物”，表示“（歌曲）节奏非常非常慢，拘谨得惊人，有时在共振钢琴音符里头漂浮，管辖乐的笔触微弱，所有亮点都集中在史密斯那强烈的控制步调上升的颤音，以及大胆副歌收尾的张力中”<ref>{{cite web|title=Writing's on the Wall: 'Sam Smith's monster Bond ballad'|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/film/james-bond-spectre/sam-smith-writings-on-the-wall-song-review/|website=The Telegraph|date=2015-09-25|access-date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122070004/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/film/james-bond-spectre/sam-smith-writings-on-the-wall-song-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 商业表现 ==
在英国，截至2015年10月8日，歌曲成为第一支位列榜首的邦德主题曲。此前高排位的邦德主题曲是阿黛尔的〈[[空降危機_(歌曲)|空降危機]]〉和[[杜兰杜兰|杜兰杜兰]]的〈{{le|雷霆杀机 (歌曲)|A View to a Kill (song)|雷霆杀机}}〉，均位列第二。这也成为史密斯两年来第五首英国冠军单曲。在美国，歌曲在[[公告牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]上以第71位首次亮相，而相较于上一首邦德主题曲《空降危機》，在2012年10月则以第8位首秀。在加拿大，歌曲以第43位首秀。而在澳大利亚，歌曲表现中肯，首秀第44位。但在爱尔兰，歌曲是一首更加热门的歌曲，首秀和最高排位都是第9位。歌曲还名列其他欧洲国家的排行榜，但其成绩比上面的都要小。

